(Corrects to remove name of CFO from second paragraph.)  Mobile Telecommunications Co., the
Kuwaiti operator known as Zain, named Hisham Akbar as deputy
chief executive officer and chief operating officer.  The Kuwait-based company made the announcement in an e-
mailed statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
